<section class="content-area">
    <div class="content-header py-120 text-left">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm">
                    <h4 class=" mb-4">Treatment of Deep and Fine Lines</h4>
                    <p class="mb-4">As our skin ages we lose collagen, our hyaluronic acid levels diminish, and gravity takes its toll causing our skin to become less elastic and sag. This sagginess creates deeper folds around our nose and mouth and with that the onset of joules and chin creases. These overt signs of aging can be mitigated with the use of fillers specifically designed to treat these areas that are key to our expression.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="content-single mb-120">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-sm">
                <div class="image-space-main">
                    <img src="./images/restylane-refyne-defyne-product.jpg" alt="Restylane Products">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm">
                <h3>RESTYLANE REFYNE® / RESTYLANE DEFYNE®</h3>
                <p class="my-4">Restylane® Refyne and Restylane Defyne is an HA filler. It softens moderate lines and wrinkles around the nose and mouth. It is a very elastic filler, formulated using XpresHAn Technology™ to maintain your facial expression and restore a more natural look to your face. It is a good choice for thinner skinned individuals due to its enhanced flexibility and decreased volumizing properties.</p>
                <p>
                    Restylane Defyne® is less elastic and thicker (cohesive) than its counterpart, REFYNE.  It provides support, adds volume and maintains natural facial expression using XpresHAn Technology™. It effectively treats deeper lines and wrinkles around the nose and mouth.
                </p>
                <hr />
                <p>Refyne Procedure</p>
                <p class="service-time">30 minutes</p>
                <p class="dull">Lasts approximately 12 - 18 months</p>
                <p>Defyne Procedure</p>
                <p class="service-time">30 MINUTE PROCEDURE</p>
                <p class="dull">Lasts approximately 1 year</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
