                <h3>JUVEDERM XC</h3>
                <p class="my-4">Juvederm XC is a HA filler that was FDA approved in 2006 so its longevity is a tribute to its results! It is more cohesive (thicker) than VOLLURE so it is better able to effectively treat deeper lines and wrinkles around the nose and mouth. Its formulation provides support, volume and elasticity.</p>
                <p class="service-time">30 MINUTE PROCEDURE</p>
                <p class="dull">Lasts approximately 1 year</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm">
